"{\"uid\": \"pasoroblesdailynews.com-tip-a-cop-event-to-raise-funds-for-special-olympics-athletes-197164\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  - ThePaso Robles Police Departmentwill host its annual \\\"Tip-A-Cop\\\" fundraiser on Sept. 18 at the Paso Robles Event Center to benefit Special Olympics Southern California.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 172, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 99, \"end\": 123, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paso_Robles_Event_Center\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paso Robles Event Center\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paso_Robles_Event_Center\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paso_Robles_Event_Center\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The event is part of a statewide initiative that involves law enforcement officers serving dinner to raise funds and awareness for Special Olympics athletes.\", \"from\": 173, \"to\": 330, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 304, \"end\": 320, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.175957994760877e-25, \"text\": \"Special Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The event features two seating times, at 5:30 p.m. and 7 p.m. A table for eight is available for $250, and individual meals for pick-up are also an option for those unable to attend.\", \"from\": 332, \"to\": 514, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"All proceeds will support Special Olympics programs in San Luis Obispo County, which provide opportunities for athletes with intellectual disabilities to participate in year-round sports, health, and community activities.\", \"from\": 515, \"to\": 736, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 541, \"end\": 557, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Special_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.175957994760877e-25, \"text\": \"Special Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], 